snippet: Sean Parker’s Scare| A Summer Davos for Women?| Zell’s Next Move
lead_paragraph: A Crazy Night in Davos Sean Parker, who helped build Napster and Facebook, had to be rushed to the hospital in Davos on his first night there after he had an allergic reaction to nuts. Henry Blodget has a compelling, if rambling, account. Business Insider
